title: City of Tampa to Host Job Fair for Veterans and Persons with Disabilities (Tampa Police ...
text: ( Source : Tampa Police Department ) On Thursday, November 12 , 2015 , the City of Tampa 's Mayor 's Alliance for Persons with Disabilities will host a job fair for veterans and persons with disabilities. Employers are invited to register online
